                  </hi>. I am a solicitor's clerk, and live in Marylebone-street. About five o'clock, on the llth of April, I was going through Tokenhouse-yard—I heard the footsteps of three parties behind me—as soon as one had passed me his appearance excited my suspicion—I put my hand to my pocket, and missed my handkerchief—this produced is it—the three all started—the prisoner was one of them.</p>
